Included files:
	-nbody_omp.c:					The final OpenMP code
	-nbody_cuda.cu:					The final CUDA code

	-timer.h & gputimer.h			Libraries for measuring time

	-custom_sem.c & custom_sem.h:	Custom semaphore library for pthreads

	-verification.py & avg.py:		Scripts for comparison with golden solution vs our code and calculation of average throughput and execution time

	-HPC_LAB5_REPORT.pdf:			Report explaining the code development process and results evaluation

	-README:						This file


Compilation instructions:
	-nbody_omp.c:					icx -Ofast nbody_omp.c -o nbody_omp -qopenmp

	-nbody_cuda.cu:					nvcc -O4 nbody_cuda.cu custom_sem.c -o nbody_cuda
